import Head from 'next/head'
import Wrapper from './Wrapper'
import Nav from '../components/Nav'
import Footer from '../components/Footer'
export default ({ children, title = 'This is the default title' }) => (
    <Wrapper>
      <Head>
        <title>{ title }</title>
      </Head>
      <header>
        <Nav />
      </header>
  
      <main>
        { children }
      </main>
  
      <Footer>
        Footer
      </Footer>
    </Wrapper>
  )
